    "To examine the effectiveness of the proposed model in reconstructing the spatial variability of phase-averaged skin-friction drags, the p.d.f.",
    "of normalized τ ν for both ML predictions and empirical measurements is depicted in figure 8 (c) for the W1-05 case with a wind speed of 5.08 m s -1.",
    "As illustrated, the p.d.f.",
    "plots of the reconstructed viscous stress align remarkably with those derived from the experimental data, particularly for the case of moderately forced wind waves.",
    "This agreement is also observed for other cases, including the high wind speed cases (not shown here for brevity)."
